        <abstract>
            The database contains data on plants registered in the geobotanical descriptions of the territory of the Ulytsia River valley, which is part of the Desniansko-Starohutskyi National Nature Park (NNP). The materials were partially included in the project of creating the mentioned NNP and were used in the allocation of protected and recreational functional zones. The database contains data on the findings of 426 species of higher vascular plants and bryophytes.
        </abstract>
